data.description: Introducing a gem located in a serene enclave of the Festival Foothills community! Situated on a coveted corner lot, this residence offers a 3-car garage & solar panels. Discover a sweeping great room, 3 generously sized bedrooms, & 2.5 pristine bathrooms. The eat-in kitchen boasts a roomy walk-in pantry, sleek quartz counters, a central island for prep or dining, ample cabinetry, & top-tier appliances. Split primary bedroom comes with an ensuite featuring dual sinks & a walk-in closet and plantation shutters throughout the home. The meticulously crafted backyard has lush artificial turf, a covered patio is perfect for relaxation, & a Ramada for shaded lounging or entertaining. Don't miss the opportunity to reside where every day feels like a festival of comfort & elegance!
